shaft 's big score ( also known as shaft 's big score ) is a 1972 american blaxploitation film starring richard basehart , moses gunn , and rosalind miles . the film was released in the united states on september 13 , 1972 . the film was followed by shaft 's big score , and was also nominated for the academy award for best foreign language film at the 87th academy awards , but was not accepted as a nominee .